Development with Android Gingerbread and Eclipse
This tutorial describes how to create Android applications with Eclipse. 
It is based on Eclipse 3.7 (Indigo), Java 1.6 and Android 2.3.3 (Gingerbread). 
http://www.vogella.de/articles/Android/article.html

